# Twelve Doors — the narrator: hard-synced saw pair on the ARP
# circuit (clean bite against the Moog bed). Oscillator two is the
# synced slave — its pitch is AUTOMATED across the song, so the
# voice's vowel changes as the story does: settled, brighter,
# pinched in the bridge, then rising continuously through the
# transformation.
